docs/design/2026-04-27-synthetic-playtest-implementation-plan.md:10:**Architecture:** Adds `runSynthPlaytest` (synchronous harness driving a `World` via pluggable `Policy` functions for `N` ticks → `SessionBundle`), three built-in policies (`noopPolicy`, `randomPolicy`, `scriptedPolicy`), shared `PolicyContext` / `StopContext` types with seeded sub-RNG, and a discriminated-union `PolicyCommand`. Extends `SessionRecorderConfig` with optional `sourceKind?` and `policySeed?` (additive); widens `SessionMetadata.sourceKind` from `'session' | 'scenario'` to `'session' | 'scenario' | 'synthetic'` (b-bump per AGENTS.md compile-breaking rule). Non-poisoned bundles with `ticksRun ≥ 1` round-trip through `SessionReplayer.selfCheck()`.
